{"tid":2155795,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫學界多個組織促政府將新型肺炎列為職業病","createTime":"2020-08-14T04:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T04:30:01.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a87d7544fed0b3f396c636be9fa0dacfa33d446","tid":2155795,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"醫學界立法會議員陳沛然、公共醫療醫生協會、醫學會及前線醫生聯盟發表聯合聲明，要求將新型肺炎列入職業病。<br />\n<br />\n聲明引述國際工會聯合會表示，由於有院內感染的證據，各國政府應將新型肺炎列為職業病，以保障照顧者的勞工權益。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543688-20200814.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543688-20200814.htm&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRxw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=691ebfd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543688-20200814.htm&h=4de65f0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543688-20200814.htm</a>"}]}